data.description: Back on the market, no fault of seller's! Beautiful, 5 bed 3 bath home sitting on 9 acres. This community is set up of mini farms. 2800 sq ft + has split floor plan, master on main floor, separate tub and shower. The living room boasts a wood burning fireplace! Lots of counter space in the kitchen and steps away from dining room. Large 2 car garage detached from home as well. HVAC unit replaced 2015, several windows replaced 2016, termite bond, 2 water heaters. Don’t miss out on this beautiful home, your oasis awaits you!
